  CE_PATH←CALLENV.⎕PATH                

⍝ Utilities
  Pad←{⍺←10 ⋄ ⍺>≢⍵:⍵↑⍨-⍺ ⋄ ⍵}
  DebugMsg←{⍺←0 ⋄ oDebug∨⍺: ⎕←'∆REQ: ',⍵ ⋄ 1:_←⍬}
  WarnMsg←{⍺←0 ⋄ oWarn∨⍺: ⎕←'∆REQ Warning: ',⍵ ⋄ 1:_←⍬}
  ExpandSearchToPath←{UP←⊂,'↑' ⋄ env path0←⍺ ⍵
      path←' '(≠⊆⊢)env.⎕PATH
      GetRef←path0∘{∪⍺,(0≠≢¨⍵)/⍵}{6::⍬ ⋄ 9=⎕NC'⍵':⍵ ⋄ ⍎⍵}¨  ⍝ Returns ns ref from string or ref, else ⍬
