   ⍝ Scan for objs in APL namespaces <memPath>, unless oForce.   If found, skip filesys scan.
 :If ~oForce
     :For i :In ⍳≢objs   ⍝ Search memPath namespaces for <obj>
         obj←i⊃objs
         :For mem :In memPath
             found←×mem.⎕NC obj         ⍝ found ∊ 1 (found), 0 (not found), ¯1 (malformed name)
             :If 0≠found                ⍝ 1 or ¯1
                 status[i]←found
                 :If found=1
